# ── Pitfalls ──
@pitfall PI-AUTO-LIVE-01 s1_call() uses curl shell-out; interpreter parse_float may mis-read floats without leading space — s1_extract_json_float() trims tail before scan.
@pitfall PI-AUTO-LIVE-02 PhiVec.raw stores full response for audit; selftest trace export does NOT dump raw by default (size), only parsed dims — raw retained in-memory only.
@pitfall PI-AUTO-LIVE-03 streak counter resets ONLY on non-negative phi_delta (0 counts as reset). If phi plateaus at 0 forever, selftest still PASSes up to depth; phi_delta=0 is NOT a regression signal per spec.

